name: "Crackle-Clatter Cryptex"
description:
A seemingly haphazard yet intricately designed cryptex, proudly crafted by the "Clink-Clank Krumkake Craftshop."
Enter the correct password "1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6" to unlock the device, whereupon a firecracker will burst forth from its dragon-mouth-shaped opening.
It is said this design was inspired by the suggestion of a certain Grand Master, seeking to evoke the thrill of a triumphant "Stage Cleared!"
"The sender said: Surprises are best saved till the end. Ha, ha, ha."
